<P><H1 align=center>ALIAS / ASSOCIATION DETAILS – DC033</H1>
<P align=center></P>
<P><FONT color=red><STRONG>NOTE: </STRONG>fields shown in red are mandatory and must be completed to 
proceed</FONT>           </P>
<P>This screen is used to registered any previous names of the applicant has 
had.</P>
<P><H3>Title / Forenames / Surname: </H3>complete the fields 
with the previous title and name.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Alias Type: </H3>this is a drop-down list – select the 
relevant reason (alias or association).
<P></P>
<P><H3>Date of Change: </H3>complete this field with the date 
the name was changed.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Method of Change: </H3>select from the drop-down list 
why and how the name was changed. Eg. marriage, divorce, by deed poll, adoption 
etc. 
<P></P>
<P><H3>OK: </H3>once details have been completed for all 
previous names, click on ‘OK’ to return to Personal Details (DC030) the previous 
screen.
<P></P>

